Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.82,0:22:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you said it's lonely\Nto go to the festival alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.18,0:22:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I smell ikayaki! You're treating!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.95,0:22:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait Sakura-chan!
