Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.65,0:22:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- Takoyaki!\N- Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.52,0:22:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yo-Yo fishing!\N- Roger...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.52,0:22:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yay, candy apple!\N- I'm cashed-out...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.85,0:22:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gotten quiet, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.98,0:22:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- Huh?!\N- Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.98,0:22:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- It can't be a ghost...\N- Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.42,0:22:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.95,0:22:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.02,0:22:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.72,0:22:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.28,0:23:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.02,0:23:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope we can see the fireworks together\Nlike this next year too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.15,0:23:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
